Name: LaserCat
About the game: Jump, dodge and explore in the search for your Owlfriend, who has been kidnapped by Wizzord: the magic space frog! A silly platform adventure inspired by classic ZX Spectrum games like Jet Set Willy! 225 rooms of non-linear exploration! Trivia questions to solve! Search through Wizzord's castle, avoid nasty enemies, find the keys and save your Owlfriend!
